# Environment Variables

Copy to `.env.local`:

```env
# Supabase (required for production auth + sync)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# Server-only: manager creates staff accounts from dashboard
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key

# ImgBB — product & logo image uploads (server-only)
# Get your key at https://api.imgbb.com/
IMGBB_API_KEY=your-imgbb-api-key

# App
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
```

Without Supabase credentials the app cannot authenticate users. Business data syncs to Supabase when configured.
